The [applicant] / [respondent] shall discharge as and when each payment becomes due, be solely responsible for and in any event indemnify the [respondent] / [applicant] against the following extra-curricular expenses of the child[ren]:

[insert (e.g. non-school extra-curricular activities such as clubs, tuition, music lessons etc.)].

Undertaking to discharge arrears

The [applicant] / [respondent] shall discharge by [date], be solely responsible for and in any event indemnify the [respondent] / [applicant] against:

the arrears which have accrued in respect of the policy with [name of company] numbered [policy number];

the arrears which have accrued in respect of the hire purchase agreement with [name of company] numbered [agreement number] in respect of the [family car] / [new car] / [car make and model] with registration number [reg. number];

the arrears which have accrued in respect of the loan agreement with [name of company] numbered [agreement number] in respect of [insert];

[etc].

Undertaking to use best endeavours to secure release from liabilities

The [applicant] / [respondent] shall use [his] / [her] best endeavours to obtain the consent of each creditor to release the [respondent] / [applicant] from any liability in respect of the following:

the hire purchase agreement with [name of company] numbered [agreement number] in respect of the [family car] / [car make and model] with registration number [reg. number];

the loan agreement with [name of company] numbered [agreement number] in respect of [insert];

[etc].

